<div style="position:absolute;left:38.40px;top:575.34px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">2.  </span><span class="cls_008">例</span><span class="cls_007">：  </span><span class="cls_008">メモは</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">どこですか。</span></div>
