<div style="position:absolute;left:302.40px;top:718.14px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">はい、もう  買って  あります。</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:201.60px;top:734.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">じ  かん</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:254.40px;top:734.94px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">し</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:64.80px;top:738.54px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">1)</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:104.40px;top:738.54px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">パーティーの</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">時間は</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_008">知らせましたか。</span><span class="cls_007">  </span><span class="cls_009">→</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:238.80px;top:755.34px" class="cls_011"><span class="cls_011">なら</span></div>
